      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLING YOUR A GAME (6) kicked off his career in good style a week ago, racing parked but sticking on to be beaten 1.5 metres into second at this circuit and distance. Draws wider but is open to natural improvement so with even luck can go one better. LA SAUVAGE (1) is a two-year-old colt by King Of Swing on debut for Gemma Hewitt. Has looked above average at the trials, winning his latest hitout. Likely to get all the favours from the inside draw so could kick off with a win. YIPPEE KIYAY (2) was beaten only 2.8 metres on debut last week. Draws well again so can progress. ROCKY HUNTER (7) draws wide but there was merit in the debut third. Strips fitter and with luck can play a role.",
